# Architecture & Stack — web_app

## Stack
- TypeScript, React 18+, Vite or CRA existing setup
- TanStack Query, react-hook-form, Zod
- Next.js rules apply where relevant; avoid heavy CSR if SSR/SSG possible

## Architecture
- Feature-first structure with shared modules
- `services/` for API clients and business logic; pure, testable functions
- `components/` for dumb/presentational components; named exports
- `pages/` for route-level composition (if applicable)
- `hooks/` for reusable hooks (no business side-effects inside)
- `lib/` for utils, constants, types

## Directories
- kebab-case names: `components/auth-wizard`, `services/user-profile`
- Each feature: `index.tsx` (exported component), `subcomponents/`, `helpers/`, `static/`, `types.ts`

## Exports
- Named exports for components and helpers
- Barrel files allowed only at feature root